author: leggat
body:
Introducing QTests and summary maps for the phase 1 pixel.

Currently monitored variables:
 -Number of clusters
 -Number of digis
 -Cluster width
 -Cluster charge
 -ADC

More information at https://twiki.cern.ch/twiki/bin/view/CMS/Phase1Summaries
title: Pixel Phase 1 summary maps
